T10TD4171E:193a-4: byang chub sems dpa' 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T10TD4171E:193a-5: dka' thub rnyed pa'i bde ba 'dod rnams kyis //
T10TD4171E:193a-6: 'chol bar spyod pa rnams ni mthong gyur pa //
T10TD4171E:193a-7: rab tu dben pa yang dag bsten pa yi //
T10TD4171E:193a-8: dge slong 'di skad tshig tu brjod pas smra //
T10TD4171E:193a-9: phongs pa spang phyir de bzhin gshegs pa yis //
T10TD4171E:193a-10: rab bsngags zhi ba'i dbang bskur nyer blangs nas //
T10TD4171E:193a-11: dka' thub khyim dang 'dris pas rab chags pa'i //
T10TD4171E:193a-12: phongs nyid rgal dka' bying ba ji lta bur //
T10TD4171E:193a-13: 'phags pa 'gran med shing drung gnas nas ni //
T10TD4171E:193a-14: 'gro ba skye dang 'gag pa mthong bas na //
T10TD4171E:193a-15: zhi ba'i bde ba yongs smin tshe dge ba //
T10TD4171E:193a-16: mi las shin tu 'phags pa thob par 'gyur //
T10TD4171E:193a-17: sems kyi rnam par 'ching ba gnyen po yi //
T10TD4171E:193a-18: stobs kyis bsal bas skye bral nags dag tu //
T10TD4171E:193a-19: rnal 'byor nyer zhi'i bdud rtsis tshim gyur pas //
T10TD4171E:193a-20: bde bar gnyid log pa dang sad par 'gyur //
T10TD4171E:193a-21: mtshan mo zla ba'i snad dang rab gsal ba'i //
T10TD4171E:193a-22: skar ma'i me tog bkram par nyer mchod nas //
T10TD4171E:193a-23: dgon par brten pa'i yid ni nges zhi ba'i //
T10TD4171E:193a-24: lhag par dga' ba dag ni skye bar 'gyur //
T10TD4171E:193a-25: gang du dge slong dben pa'i rgyu mtshan gyis //
T10TD4171E:193a-26: kha na ma tho med pa zhi 'gyur bde //
T10TD4171E:193a-27: gang du ye byad yang dag bsten chags pas //
T10TD4171E:193a-28: sems ni sna tshogs phongs pas gdungs par 'gyur //
T10TD4171E:193a-29: ji ltar chu shing smyug ma 'od ma dag /'bras bu 'byin nas rang nyid 'jig pa ston //
T10TD4171E:193a-30: de bzhin dka' thub khyim las rnam grol nas //
T10TD4171E:193b-0: bdag nyid zil gyis gnon la @193b chags mthong 'gyur //
T10TD4171E:193b-1: sa yi rdul gyis gos pa'i ri dags dag / rtsva dang 'dab nas tsam zhig sgrub byed ltar //
T10TD4171E:193b-2: sems ni dben par gzhol ba 'dod 'gyur gyi //
T10TD4171E:193b-3: gling bzhi'i phun tshogs rgya chen dag la 'ang min //
T10TD4171E:193b-4: shing drung 'bab chu bstan pa'i dka' thub dag / yongs su 'dzin pa dag ni rnam spangs nas //
T10TD4171E:193b-5: rang sems tsam dang rab tu 'brel pa yi ;
T10TD4171E:193b-6: / bde 'byung gang de rgyal po rnams la med //
T10TD4171E:193b-7: ljon shing sngon po'i rtse mo rlung dag gis //
T10TD4171E:193b-8: rnam g-yo phra la snyoms pa'i char 'bab pa'i //
T10TD4171E:193b-9: mi g-yo rnam brtags ri yi sul gnas ni //
T10TD4171E:193b-10: dge slong mtshan mo dge ba skyed par byed //
T10TD4171E:193b-11: rnyog can 'dod la 'dris pas 'phos pa yi //
T10TD4171E:193b-12: bdag bsnyen pa yi chags spangs ltos med cing //
T10TD4171E:193b-13: skye bral nags gang yin par dga' bya yi //
T10TD4171E:193b-14: dge slong gyur nas don med 'gyur mi bya //
T10TD4171E:193b-15: dge slong rtags ni bdag nyid gnod med par //
T10TD4171E:193b-16: nyer blangs gang zhig sgrub par mi byed cing //
T10TD4171E:193b-17: dman la yongs su 'dzin pa'i 'dam bying ba //
T10TD4171E:193b-18: de ni 'tsho ba'i 'jig rten slu byed yin //
T10TD4171E:193b-19: chu dang rdo khu rtsa ba med pa yi //
T10TD4171E:193b-20: sa dbang 'dzegs nas mi bzad yang dag tu //
T10TD4171E:193b-21: rtog dang ldan pas shib bzod bya yi //
T10TD4171E:193b-22: bslab pa yongs su nyams pas 'jug mi bya //
T10TD4171E:193b-23: rgya mtsho rnam par 'khrugs pa'i rlabs tshogs su //
T10TD4171E:193b-24: rin chen khur gyis gru dag nub pa bzhin //
T10TD4171E:193b-25: khyim dang 'dris pa'i rnyed chags khur dag gis //
T10TD4171E:193b-26: gang dag mchog brten rgya chen snub par byed //
T10TD4171E:193b-27: nags na brten pa'i zhi ba'i ri dags ni //
T10TD4171E:193b-28: gzhon nu ma yi 'gro bas dkrugs mtshon pa //
T10TD4171E:193b-29: gnyen po 'ji bzhin bdag nyid zhi 'dod rnams //
T10TD4171E:193b-30: sdom can rab tu dben nyid yang dag rtsom //
T10TD4171E:193b-31: yul gyi ro yi dug gis nyer gdung blo can dag / chags pa nyung ngu dag gis gdung gyur na //
T10TD4171E:193b-32: de dag yongs su spong la rtsod med pa'i //
T10TD4171E:193b-33: dka' thub kyi hud ae ma'o rab nyams 'gyur //
T10TD4171E:193b-34: sdom can rkang pas 'gro zhing 'jog pa ltar ;
T10TD4171E:193b-36: rang rlabs chab dogs mngon brdabs 'jigs rung bas //
T10TD4171E:193b-37: sprin chen char gyis ya mu na bzhin no //
T10TD4171E:193b-38: dka' thub ji ltar dman pa dag la yang //
T10TD4171E:193b-39: 'dod lha'i dbang gis rjes su zhugs gyur pa //
T10TD4171E:193b-40: de ltar rang lag gis drang phun sum tshogs //
T10TD4171E:193b-41: rgyal chen khyim la khyim pa chags pa med //
T10TD4171E:193b-42: rang gi khyim dang gdong dag mchi 'dzag pas //
T10TD4171E:193b-43: brlan pa'i gnyen dag spangs par gyur nas ni //
T10TD4171E:193b-44: dman pa gzhan gyi khyim la chags pa yi //
T10TD4171E:193b-45: rab byung 'di la shin tu ngo tsha med //
T10TD4171E:193b-46: thar pa 'dod gang rang khyim spangs nas ni //
T10TD4171E:193b-47: mi shes gzhan gyi khyim dag 'dod byed pa //
T10TD4171E:193b-48: rgya mtsho rnam par 'khrugs pa'i rlabs tshogs las //
T10TD4171E:194a-0: bdag nyid rgal nas glang rjes @194a * //
T10TD4171E:194a-2: sdig pa spong byed de bzhin gshegs pa yis //
T10TD4171E:194a-3: gnang ba'i sgrub pa dag gis 'di brtags gang //
T10TD4171E:194a-4: dman pa'i nor la 'dod pa'i sred pa yis //
T10TD4171E:194a-5: gzhan khyim la chags dri ma can du 'gyur //
T10TD4171E:194a-6: chu bo ni lu tsha yi me tog lhung ba'i dum bus mtha' mar bris //
T10TD4171E:194a-7: bye ma dkar po'i dogs dang ngang pa ka dam pa dag gnas //
T10TD4171E:194a-8: nags kyi glang chen khyu dag rtse bas tha dad 'thor rlabs can //
T10TD4171E:194a-9: dgon gnas brtul zhugs can la dga' ba rab tu skyed par byed //
T10TD4171E:194a-10: srid pa'i longs spyod don du gnyer ba'i yi dags rnams bsal nas //
T10TD4171E:194a-11: ma brtsams yid 'ong bde ba bsten pa rnams kyi gnas skabs ni //
T10TD4171E:194a-12: padma kha bye bzhin du dka' thub rang gi grags pa yis //
T10TD4171E:194a-13: 'jig rten yongs su dga' ba rab skyed kun du dpe las 'das //
T10TD4171E:194a-14: dka' thub ri dang nye ba'i shing rtsa rab yangs dang 'brel bar //
T10TD4171E:194a-15: gnas pa'i chom bu mi snyoms lhod pa'i srubs bar la chags pa'i //
T10TD4171E:194a-16: ba mo'i dum bus gos pa tho rangs nyi ma'i 'od zer gyis //
T10TD4171E:194a-17: lag pa dag gis nyul ba bzhin du rnam par skems par byed //
T10TD4171E:194a-18: khang stong shing drung rlung ni rgyu gyur kha ba'i tshogs chen 'bab //
T10TD4171E:194a-19: mdangs zad rab rtsub lo ma dag gis gdu bu bzhin bskor ba'i //
T10TD4171E:194a-20: 'dod pa kun spangs shes rab rno ba'i brtul zhugs can dag la //
T10TD4171E:194a-21: mtshan mo rnam par skyo ba dag ni skyed par zad mi byed //
T10TD4171E:194a-22: shing gi lo ma'i tha ma la chags ba mo'i chu dag gi / dum bu nyi ma 'char tshe mdog nor bu dang 'dra //
T10TD4171E:194a-23: thigs pa dag ni shing drung gnas pa'i dge slong la //
T10TD4171E:194a-24: 'gro ba'i skye dang 'jig pa ji bzhin rab tu ston par byed //
T10TD4171E:194a-25: rab zhi'i bde ro shes pas 'khor los sgyur ba'i dpal 'byor kyang //
T10TD4171E:194a-26: yongs su dpyad pas rnyings pa'i me tog phreng bzhin rnam spangs nas //
T10TD4171E:194a-27: lang tsho rang bzhin gyis g-yo ngang tshul can dag yol byas te //
T10TD4171E:194a-28: dgon par ri dags 'drar 'chi zhi ba'i sems ni brtan par bya //
T10TD4171E:194a-29: 'dod pa la 'jen phyin ci log pa'i sems la ku mu ta'i //
T10TD4171E:194a-30: dum bu ltar dkar mi thod so dang 'brel pas nyer dgod dang //
T10TD4171E:194a-31: rlung gis bud pa'i ro bsregs me yis nye 'khor shing bsregs pa'i //
T10TD4171E:194a-32: dur khrod dka' thub gcig pu la ni mtshan mo dga' ba skyed par byed //
T10TD4171E:194a-33: ljon shing tshogs dang rgya ches ri yi rtsa ba sngor gyur cing //
T10TD4171E:194a-34: rdo bas khyab dang bsil la rab dang ba yi chu 'dzag 'bab //
T10TD4171E:194a-35: rma bya rab dga' sgra yis khyab pa'i ri sul nang du ni //
T10TD4171E:194a-36: khyim du 'chi ba'i skyo ba'i sems ni rab tu dga' bar byed //
T10TD4171E:194a-37: 'gro ba'i don ma byas pa'i 'chi bar 'gyur ba khyim dag la //
T10TD4171E:194b-0: dga' ba dag la dben pa mchog la slob @194b byed sems can mchog / rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems ni rnyed gyur pha rol tshogs 'thob pa //
T10TD4171E:194b-1: srid pa'i dug gi sdong po'i rtsa ba brtan po 'byin par byed //
T10TD4171E:194b-2: nags tshig pa yi bya dang 'dra bar sdug bsngal brgya yi gzhir gyur pa'i //
T10TD4171E:194b-3: khyim gang yin pa yongs su spangs nas nags su 'gro byed pa //
T10TD4171E:194b-4: des ni srid pa'i gnyid rab bsal ba 'gro ba kun gyi mgon //
T10TD4171E:194b-5: sangs rgyas rab tu mnyes par byed pa yin zhes de skad grags //
T10TD4171E:194b-6: mrgad sngon po dang 'dra ne'u gseng tshogs dag ni //
T10TD4171E:194b-7: shing rtsa nye bar bkod dang yal ga me tog gis bskor ba'i //
T10TD4171E:194b-8: zhi ba'i nags mtha' kye ma'o dge slong mchog gis spong byed pa //
T10TD4171E:194b-9: gsad phyir rngon pa'i glu yis drangs par gyur pa'i ri dags mtshungs //
T10TD4171E:194b-10: 'phags pa'i bzhed pa bde bar gshegs pa'i lam gyi rjes 'brangs nas //
T10TD4171E:194b-11: nags dang 'dra bar khyim gyi rang gi don dag sgrub byed kyang //
T10TD4171E:194b-12: rnam par 'tshe ba rang bzhin gyis med nags ni dben pa yis //
T10TD4171E:194b-13: sems kyi 'ching ba dag ni 'bad pa med par gcod par byed //
T10TD4171E:194b-14: 'dod chags gang dag de la dgos par 'gyur bas kun 'phel zhing //
T10TD4171E:194b-15: legs spyad thub pa'i bstan pa dag kyang nyams byas nas //
T10TD4171E:194b-16: me dpung rab tu 'bar ba rgal dka'i khongs ni mthar thug pa'i //
T10TD4171E:194b-17: ngan song dag tu dge slong bde chung la chags 'gro bar 'gyur //
T10TD4171E:194b-18: gang zhig nyes pa ma lus gdung ba zad byed sangs rgyas pa'i //
T10TD4171E:194b-19: legs par bshad pa khas blangs nas ni ngan 'gror ngan 'byin pa //
T10TD4171E:194b-20: autpal sngon po'i snying po'i dri mchog dag dang chu dum bu //
T10TD4171E:194b-21: sar la bsil ldan rlung gis de dag ji ltar tshim par 'gyur //
T10TD4171E:194b-22: sa ra sa yi sgra ni rang bzhin snyan pa'i glu dbyangs dag / ldog pa med par sgrogs par gyur pas mchog rnams khyab gyur pas //
T10TD4171E:194b-23: brtul zhugs can gyis 'gro dang gnas pa dag las dub skyes dang //
T10TD4171E:194b-24: lus lhod gyur pa'i mtshan gyi gung thun gnyid dag sad par byed //
T10TD4171E:194b-25: rang gi 'od kyi dkyil 'khor gyis spras yongs su gnas pa yis //
T10TD4171E:194b-26: zla ba'i 'od zer tshogs kyi dpal 'joms shin tu zil gnon pas //
T10TD4171E:194b-27: dge ba'i rtsa ba nyer bsags skal ldan 'jig rten la gzigs shing //
T10TD4171E:194b-28: rang byung 'phags pa mchog ni dgon pa de yang sten par mdzad ;
T10TD4171E:194b-29: / ci ste gang zhig nang gi dgra las nges rgyal bya ba byas pa yi //
T10TD4171E:194b-30: ston pa 'jig rten mtha' gzigs de yang nags dag sten mdzad na //
T10TD4171E:194b-31: yang dag mi rtogs skye bo mi gtsang 'dam du bying gyur pa'i //
T10TD4171E:194b-32: sdom can zhi 'dod bde gshegs rjes su ci phyir 'jug mi byed //
T10TD4171E:194b-33: bdag tu log par 'dzin par gyur pas nyin dang mtshan //
T10TD4171E:195a-1: bzhin rnam rtog sdig can dag gis zos pas na //
T10TD4171E:195a-2: nyon mongs rnag gis nyer gos zhi ba'i chu yi bum pa yis //
T10TD4171E:195a-3: bkrus pa bzhin du sems ni skye ba med nags bsten par gyis //
T10TD4171E:195a-4: 'bras bu'i lcid kyis yal ga gug pa'i tham lo ma yis //
T10TD4171E:195a-5: gsal gyur lcug ma me tog kha bye'i dga' byed rgyu ldan pa'i //
T10TD4171E:195a-6: nags kyi shing ni dge slong phongs bral bsten pa la //
T10TD4171E:195a-7: mdza' bo bzhin du shin tu dbugs ni 'byin par byed //
T10TD4171E:195a-8: zla ba shar ba kha ba 'bab pa bsgrigs pas 'gog 'gyur ba'i //
T10TD4171E:195a-9: dgun gyi mtshan mo dag ni rab zhi bde ba 'dod rnams kyi //
T10TD4171E:195a-10: rnal 'byor rtsva yi stan la dga' ba dag la tho rangs dag / nags kyi shing na yib pa'i bya rnams 'dra bar byed //
T10TD4171E:195a-11: shing dang nye ba'i ri yi rked du mi g-yo skyil krung bcas //
T10TD4171E:195a-12: me tog gis bskor rab dga'i rlung gis g-yo bar byed pa na //
T10TD4171E:195a-13: 'gro gnyen srid gsum rnam rgyal dus na byang chub snying po yi //
T10TD4171E:195a-14: gdan la bzhugs bzhin sdom can mtshan mo rjes su sgrub par byed //
T10TD4171E:195a-15: dman pa'i 'gro ba'i sems kyis reg byas dregs pa'i chags pa dag /'dod bya don du gnyer ba rnams kyis khyad par spangs nas ni //
T10TD4171E:195a-16: 'phags pas rjes chags brtan pa mi snang 'ching ba 'jigs pa yi //
T10TD4171E:195a-17: 'dod pa lhag ma med par dga' bzhin nags su zhi bar bya //
T10TD4171E:195a-18: skye dang 'chi dang na ba'i sdug bsngal mthar ni ma byas par //
T10TD4171E:195a-19: srid pa'i rgya mtsho dag tu bying 'gyur bag med ma byed cig / mthar byed kun gyi srog kyang 'phrog par byed pa gang 'di ni //
T10TD4171E:195a-20: rgyun mi chad par 'gro la sta re'i so dag 'dar bar byed //
T10TD4171E:195a-21: sa 'dzin pa yi chu bo'i tshogs dag 'bab pa lta bu ni //
T10TD4171E:195a-22: chos kun gnas pa'i rang bzhin rjes su shes nas ni //
T10TD4171E:195a-23: ro la sems ldan gzhan las dam pas legs par 'gro ba yis //
T10TD4171E:195a-24: srid la chags bral rab zhi dga' ba dag la brten par gyis //
T10TD4171E:195a-25: smra ba tsam ni nus su zin kyang tshig la gnas pa 'ang grub med de //
T10TD4171E:195a-26: skyes bu tshig dang snying por byed pa ston gyi chu bral sprin dang mtshungs //
T10TD4171E:195a-27: gang phyir de bzhin gshegs pa'i bstan pa 'di la sgrub pa snying po nyid //
T10TD4171E:195a-28: de phyir de nyid la 'jug blo gros yin bzo'i tshig la mkhas //
T10TD4171E:195a-29: kun nas nyon mongs dgra 'di yi //
T10TD4171E:195a-30: bdag nyid bran du gyur pa ste //
T10TD4171E:195a-31: de bas bdag sems zhi byed cing //
T10TD4171E:195a-32: rang nyid yongs su smra bar byed //
T10TD4171E:195a-33: dben pa'i gtam slob dpon chen pos 'tsho byin gyis mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T10TD4171E:195a-35: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po d'i pam ka ra dang /
T10TD4171E:195a-36: zhu chen gyi lo ts'a ba dge slong dge ba'i blo gros kyis bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o /
